properties.name: camel.dataformat.swift-mt.enabled
properties.description: Whether to enable auto configuration of the swiftMt data format. This is enabled by default.

properties.name: camel.dataformat.swift-mt.write-in-json
properties.description: The flag indicating that messages must be marshalled in a JSON format.

properties.name: camel.dataformat.swift-mx.enabled
properties.description: Whether to enable auto configuration of the swiftMx data format. This is enabled by default.

properties.name: camel.dataformat.swift-mx.read-config-ref
properties.description: Refers to a specific configuration to use when unmarshalling an input stream to lookup from the registry.

properties.name: camel.dataformat.swift-mx.read-message-id
properties.description: The type of MX message to produce when unmarshalling an input stream. If not set, it will be automatically detected from the namespace used.

properties.name: camel.dataformat.swift-mx.write-config-ref
properties.description: Refers to a specific configuration to use when marshalling a message to lookup from the registry.

properties.name: camel.dataformat.swift-mx.write-in-json
properties.description: The flag indicating that messages must be marshalled in a JSON format.
